description.plain:
Aron Michael Ekberg (AronChupa) is a rapper, singer, songwriter, DJ, record producer, and record label owner from Sweden.

Aron started his career as a soccer player, and later created an electro-hip hop group called Albatraoz (Signed to Sony Music Sweden), along with his friends/members of the soccer club he played for.

His most Popular song is “I’m an Albatroz,” and his only album so far is Russ, released in 2014.

songs.title: I’m an Albatraoz

description.plain:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bznxx12Ptl0

“I’m an Albatraoz” is the first single from a Swedish DJ / producer / song writer, Aron Michael Ekberg, known as AronChupa. He is a member of electronic hip-hop group named, Albatraoz, which the name is included in the title of his first own single, I’m an Albatraoz.

“I’m an Albatraoz” is quite viral with over 400 million views on YouTube and reached #1 on Spotify in Sweden with 9 million plays (as of Dec. 30 2015, it has over 170 million plays).



The vocalist of the song is his sister, Nora Ekberg, which the vocal is uncredited but featured in the music video.

Her scene from the music video:



Interestingly, the expletives in the song were censored on music streaming platforms in 2020 with no explanation, though Spotify mentioned that the song was originally explicit, which is why it carried the tag.
